{"tid":547723,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"卡牌遊戲Shadow Era短篇故事: Wizent的日記","createTime":"2018-02-01T17:29:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-05T17:43:50.000Z","uid":37288,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dee9ffee2d74379e68f9977567b194f0922ca473","tid":547723,"uid":37288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T17:29:44.000Z","msg":"本人由初中開始已經玩緊Shadow Era依隻game, 見住佢由得software, app, 到出實體卡, 攪比賽。到依家故事線愈來愈完整，但係香港都係hit唔起，所以想翻譯下官方出既背景故事，從而吸引人玩。今次先翻譯第一個出既背景故事，本人好耐無寫野，文筆唔太好。如有不足請多多指教。<br />\n<br />\nShadow Era 官方網站: <a href=\"http://www.shadowera.com/content.php?147-Play&amp;tabid=78\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.shadowera.com%2Fcontent.php%3F147-Play%26tabid%3D78&d=8FR%2FH2FOr0q1scos%2BgoAVqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=7481a070\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.shadowera.com/content.php?147-Play&amp;tabid=78</a><br />\nios下載: <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/shadow-era-dark-prophecies/id631262453?ls=1&amp;mt=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Fshadow-era-dark-prophecies%2Fid631262453%3Fls%3D1%26mt%3D8&d=8FR%2FH2FOr0q1scos%2BgoAVqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=6f116b37\" target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/shadow-era-dark-prophecies/id631262453?ls=1&amp;mt=8</a><br />\nAndroid下載: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.wulven.shadowera\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.wulven.shadowera&d=8FR%2FH2FOr0q1scos%2BgoAVqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=af71ac13\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.wulven.shadowera</a><br />\n<br />\nBalor地圖:<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.wulven.com/balor_map.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.wulven.com%2Fbalor_map.jpg&h=d02186d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWizent的日記&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;序<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.shadowera.com/attachment.php?attachmentid=3936&amp;d=1365821112\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.shadowera.com%2Fattachment.php%3Fattachmentid%3D3936%26d%3D1365821112&h=42aeaa29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n經過連日來的趕路，Loest已經體力透支。他父親臨終前把最後的希望託付給這位少年&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;不惜一切也要好好保護日記。但這一切也無法阻止Loest從保護套中拿出日記來閱讀。因為他一早已下定決心用自己的生命作賭注，靠自己的記憶力來保管好日記。 <br />\n<br />\nLoest的手不經意地把日記從背包中取出，並將令日記與世隔絕的繩子緩緩解開。頃刻，他停下來尋找一處茂密得不易被人察覺到的樹叢來休息。確認自己不會被發現後，他回想起日記上的繩結是Arada的大祭司在意外身亡前打上的。 <br />\n<br />\nLoest瞬間被自己的罪疚感壓得透不過氣來。他打開了日記並在當中讀到了提及他命運的段落&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;父親Wizent的遺言。這段遺言所包含的秘密，將可拯救整個Balor。 <br />\n<br />\nLoest卡牌:<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.shadowera.com/cards/sf201.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.shadowera.com%2Fcards%2Fsf201.jpg&h=a728b709&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dd86289e73f583825ceea6e106979f626beeaa4d","tid":547723,"uid":114127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T17:16:57.000Z","msg":"呢隻game係香港好泠門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f81cc33aa73dbf5b0b01b35c69f5038793503f06","tid":547723,"uid":37288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd86289e73f583825ceea6e106979f626beeaa4d","tid":547723,"uid":114127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T17:16:57.000Z","msg":"呢隻game係香港好泠門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T08:08:55.000Z","msg":"巴打有玩? 用咩英?"},{"pid":"624a00176c9f485b22a4f5efbf1ff3b572521a51","tid":547723,"uid":37288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T10:20:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本人由初中開始已經玩緊Shadow Era依隻game, 見住佢由得software, app, 到出實體卡, 攪比賽。到依家故事線愈來愈完整，但係香港都係hit唔起，所以想翻譯下官方出既背景故事，從而吸引人玩。今次先翻譯第一個出既背景故事，本人好耐無寫野，文筆唔太好。如有不足請多多指教。<br />\n<br />\nShadow Era 官方網站: <a href=\"http://www.shadowera.com/content.php?147-Play&amp;tabid=78\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww